{%- comment -%} Charmé legal/policy pages. One section, four policy bodies chosen by setting. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign t = section.settings.policy_type -%}

<div class="page-head"><div class="wrap">
  <h1>
    {%- case t -%}
      {%- when 'shipping' -%}Shipping &amp; Returns
      {%- when 'refund' -%}Refund Policy
      {%- when 'privacy' -%}Privacy Policy
      {%- when 'terms' -%}Terms of Service
      {%- else -%}{{ page.title }}
    {%- endcase -%}
  </h1>
  <div class="updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %Y' }}</div>
</div></div>

<div class="wrap"><div class="legal">
  <div class="note"><b>⚠ Placeholder</b> — Replace with Shopify's generated policy (Settings → Policies) and have it reviewed before launch. Delivery windows must match reality (FTC transparency). Not legal advice.</div>

  {%- case t -%}
  {%- when 'shipping' -%}
    <h2>Processing time</h2>
    <p>Orders are processed and dispatched within 1–2 business days. You'll receive a tracking number by email as soon as your order ships.</p>
    <h2>Delivery time</h2>
    <p>Delivery to the United States typically takes 8–15 days after dispatch. Delivery windows are estimates and can vary during peak periods and holidays. The estimated window is shown on the product page and again at checkout.</p>
    <h2>Shipping cost</h2>
    <ul><li>Free standard US shipping on orders over $35.</li><li>Orders under $35: flat-rate shipping calculated at checkout.</li></ul>
    <h2>Tracking</h2>
    <p>Every order ships with tracking. If your tracking hasn't updated within 5 business days of dispatch, contact us and we'll look into it.</p>
    <h2>Returns</h2>
    <p>We accept returns on unused items in original condition within 30 days of delivery. To start a return, email us with your order number. Return shipping is the customer's responsibility unless the item arrived damaged or incorrect.</p>
    <h2>Damaged or wrong item</h2>
    <p>If your order arrives damaged or isn't what you ordered, email us within 7 days of delivery with a photo and we'll make it right at no cost to you.</p>
    <h2>Refunds</h2>
    <p>Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method within 5–10 business days of us receiving the returned item. See our <a href="/pages/refund-policy" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">Refund Policy</a>.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about an order? Reach us via the <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- when 'refund' -%}
    <h2>30-day returns</h2>
    <p>We accept returns within 30 days of delivery on unused items in their original condition and packaging.</p>
    <h2>How to start a return</h2>
    <p>Email us with your order number and reason for return. We'll reply with return instructions. Please don't send items back before you hear from us.</p>
    <h2>Refunds</h2>
    <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, we'll email you to confirm. Approved refunds are issued to your original payment method within 5–10 business days.</p>
    <h2>Non-returnable</h2>
    <ul><li>Items marked final sale.</li><li>Used or damaged items not caused by us.</li><li>Gift cards.</li></ul>
    <h2>Damaged or defective</h2>
    <p>If your item arrives damaged or defective, contact us within 7 days with a photo. We'll send a replacement or full refund — your choice — at no cost.</p>
    <h2>Exchanges</h2>
    <p>Want a different colorway? Return the original and place a new order. It's the fastest way to get what you want.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Reach us via the <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- when 'privacy' -%}
    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>When you shop with us, we collect the information you provide — name, shipping address, email, and payment details — plus basic device and browsing data through cookies and analytics.</p>
    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <ul><li>To process and ship your order.</li><li>To send order updates and, if you opt in, marketing emails.</li><li>To improve the store and our ads.</li></ul>
    <h2>Who we share it with</h2>
    <p>We share data only with the services that run the store: our ecommerce platform (Shopify), payment processor, fulfillment partner, email tool, and advertising/analytics providers. We don't sell your personal information.</p>
    <h2>Cookies &amp; tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar tools (including advertising pixels) to run the site and measure marketing. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You can request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by emailing us. Depending on where you live, additional rights may apply.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions? Reach us via the <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- when 'terms' -%}
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>By using this website and placing an order, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the site.</p>
    <h2>Orders</h2>
    <p>We may refuse or cancel any order at our discretion, including for suspected fraud or pricing errors. If we cancel an order you've paid for, we'll refund you in full.</p>
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <p>Prices are in US dollars and may change without notice. "Compare-at" prices reference our own reference price and are not necessarily a price the item previously sold at over any period.</p>
    <h2>Products</h2>
    <p>We do our best to show colors and details accurately, but screens vary. Slight variation between the photos and the item you receive is normal.</p>
    <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>All content on this site — brand name, logo, text, and images — belongs to Charmé and may not be reused without permission.</p>
    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>To the extent permitted by law, we're not liable for indirect or incidental damages arising from use of the site or products.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms? Reach us via the <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- else -%}
    <div class="rte">{{ page.content }}</div>
  {%- endcase -%}
</div></div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Charmé Legal",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "policy_type",
      "label": "Policy",
      "options": [
        { "value": "shipping", "label": "Shipping & Returns" },
        { "value": "refund", "label": "Refund Policy" },
        { "value": "privacy", "label": "Privacy Policy" },
        { "value": "terms", "label": "Terms of Service" },
        { "value": "custom", "label": "Use page content" }
      ],
      "default": "shipping"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
